\pard\plain \tx0\tx360\tx720\tx1080\tx1440\tx1800\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\fi360\sa240\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 The Black Dragonflight brood-mother hissed in pain, swinging her head around to confront the reunified King. Bolvar Fordragon stepped up next to Varian, Raynn joining them as Mathias Shaw took charge of Anduin.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 As the last of the dragonspawn fell to their frost magic, Jaina Proudmoore and Bryna also turned to the dragon mother. Kamery knelt beside her sister, helping Carolyn to her feet, but her determined grey eyes were fixed on Onyxia. From the opposite side to Varian, Broll and Elthas padded towards the dragon from their recent skirmishes with her progeny.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Outmatched, Onyxia snarled in frustration. Snapping her wings to full span, she abruptly teleported away. A sudden silence fell on the vast room, broken only by the sound of their heavy breathing.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 As the echoes of the battle faded, Anduin ran forward to embrace his father.}}